<div class="container">

<div class="jumbotron">
	<h1 style="text-align: center;">Get Your Free TM Tickets</h1>
	<hr class="star-light">
	<p><b>Ticketmaster made it hard to claim the Class Action tickets they owe you, so let's make it easy</b></p>
	<p>Short Story: Ticketmaster is obligated to pay approximately $40M back to its customers after a class action settlement over its service fees. <b><a href="http://www.theverge.com/2016/6/21/11992004/ticketmaster-best-free-shows-tickets">The Verge</a></b> has called their strategy a "garbage fire legal settlement."</p>
