	<p>Ticketmaster put up a huge list of shows that you are eligible to attend with your Class Action vouchers. The problem: <b>the list isn't remotely searchable</b>, and it's filled with bands that you forgot in 1999. It's even been <b><a href="http://www.miaminewtimes.com/music/miamis-ticketmaster-voucher-concerts-are-like-a-christmas-present-from-your-grandma-8543153">described</a></b> as a "Christmas present... you got from your Grandma." Thanks Ticketmaster!</p>
	<p>Nonetheless, there are a few good ones hidden, and I want to help you find them. Use our tool below to filter by genre and state to find shows that might even be close to you (sorry NYC, your closest is Saratoga Springs).</p>
